  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 ; \u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0baf\u0ba3\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "covid infection; Suspension of ticketing operations at Ragama railway station",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lankan Railway Station Principals' Association has informed that the operation of issuing tickets at Ragamai Railway Station has been suspended this morning (28).",
        "The action has been taken after the master of Ragama railway station was confirmed to be infected with Covid.",
        "Sri Lanka Railway Station Managers Association has informed that relief officers will be sent today Thursday to cover the duties at the railway station."
      ],
